{"tid":813405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美網】大坂直美係美網2018頒獎禮 因觀眾對賽事的boo而say sorry","createTime":"2018-09-10T11:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T13:03:28.000Z","uid":168366,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6458d040d4fa90fc9e779b392875dd3ab03e6233","tid":813405,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCm3BemDlj8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjCm3BemDlj8&d=h9x%2FkiD%2Fjg6zPxWSC06eAsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=5ae981e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jCm3BemDlj8</a><br />\n<br />\n第一個大滿貫竟然個場面會係咁 比人boo 仲要明明佢贏 個場面迫到佢講sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2018/09/08/its-shameful-what-us-open-did-to-naomi-osaka/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2Fits-shameful-what-us-open-did-to-naomi-osaka%2F&d=h9x%2FkiD%2Fjg6zPxWSC06eAsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=0c6fbeac\" target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2018/09/08/its-shameful-what-us-open-did-to-naomi-osaka/</a><br />\n<br />\nUpon accepting her (William) finalist award, she gave parsimonious praise to her competitor while telling the crowd she felt their pain.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Let&rsquo;s try to make this the best moment we can,&rdquo; she said in part, &ldquo;and we&rsquo;ll get through it . . . let&rsquo;s not boo anymore. We&rsquo;re gonna get through this and let&rsquo;s be positive, so congratulations, Naomi.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nOsaka accepted her trophy while choking back tears. She never smiled. When asked if her childhood dream of playing against Williams matched the reality, she politely sidestepped the question.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I&rsquo;m sorry,&rdquo; Osaka said. &ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">I know that everyone was cheering for her and I&rsquo;m sorry it had to end like this.</span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nShe turned to Williams. &ldquo;I&rsquo;m really grateful I was able to play with you,&rdquo; Osaka said. &ldquo;Thank you.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"ba2fb1d6c18e62417eb8532f4e237272db2eb36a","tid":813405,"uid":7494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c21b3656430b3d2001307a39d6423d0a315c321","tid":813405,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T11:58:25.000Z","msg":"觀眾boo係因為覺得個裁判對William不公而導致佢輸左 <br />\n裁判因為William的verbal abuse(話佢thief)而判William a game penalty"},{"pid":"792f69eac602249f7f7927f0a2b9bf062d345822","tid":813405,"uid":119450,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:02:07.000Z","msg":"啲觀眾睇波上哂腦<br />\n只會捧自己偶像 不問對錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91f5b6670de5a0af6496b4accf6ac4d1cebd610","tid":813405,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa5a548dab1d222febee4ec2b7e5c545c31b235","tid":813405,"uid":35914,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:14:21.000Z","msg":"條力架唔夠人打搞事<br />\n搞到人地贏咗都變得唔光彩<br />\n明明係一個高級別嘅獎盃，條黑鬼應該要出黎道歉"},{"pid":"b50a30d57f8f04d6f28d7217600c80656d6397de","tid":813405,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"足球&gt;藍球&gt;網球"},{"pid":"7b0d047a2bbdd872960e6b9c434b401a96eb8463","tid":813405,"uid":6959,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d3a861b2ae0a2aad9ab44bbb161a558e955c47a","tid":813405,"uid":168366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7b0d047a2bbdd872960e6b9c434b401a96eb8463","tid":813405,"ui