g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b3a259bb614468a5b7527d6c0322fc3285b6c2","tid":813405,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:03:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.news.com.au/sport/tennis/naomi-osaka-explains-her-emotional-apology-at-the-us-open/news-story/a64f8dbdbca65145ef735f52ea0d2132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.com.au%2Fsport%2Ftennis%2Fnaomi-osaka-explains-her-emotional-apology-at-the-us-open%2Fnews-story%2Fa64f8dbdbca65145ef735f52ea0d2132&d=h9x%2FkiD%2Fjg6zPxWSC06eAsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=2d0a27ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.com.au/sport/tennis/naomi-osaka-explains-her-emotional-apology-at-the-us-open/news-story/a64f8dbdbca65145ef735f52ea0d2132</a><br />\n<br />\n想改title<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來今日佢接受左訪問<br />\n講點解佢會say sorry<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Because I know she really wanted to have the 24th Grand Slam, right? Everyone knows this. It&rsquo;s on the commercials, it&rsquo;s everywhere.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;When I step onto the court, I feel like a different person. I&rsquo;m not a Serena fan. I&rsquo;m just a tennis player playing another tennis player.<br />\n<br />\n佢話自己係細威係超級fans <br />\n&quot;&ldquo;She&rsquo;s the main reason why I started playing tennis and I have seen her on TV so many times and I have always been cheering for her.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nShe needed just three letters &ldquo;OMG&rdquo; to sum up the experience on Instagram. (佢同細威握手)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}